The '''Imperial Heritage Museum''' was a museum established on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] during the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. After to the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], one of its exhibits (centering on an attempted assassination of [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] by [[Vune Willic]]) was called "[[Imperial Justice: Triumph of the New Order]]."

